{"tid":1748663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然係一場造假選舉，但都要投非建制","createTime":"2019-11-23T19:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T20:49:52.000Z","uid":55378,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d202b23d6e524925cdd1a521cdc52ac86303b664","tid":1748663,"uid":55378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府有信心到咁<br />\n擺明已經下決心全力造假<br />\n反正就算有人抗議<br />\n佢都係一句無問題當人弱智<br />\n佢會做下樣控制結果係建制險勝過半數<br />\n<br />\n唯有盡人事投非建制<br />\n小心多過2個候選人既區，集中投1個<br />\n除左投票，監察都係重點<br />\n場內監察唯有靠黃既公務員pt<br />\n場外要注意調包票箱之類古惑招<br />\n<br />\n最起碼要捉到造假證據!<br />\n等班建制贏左都無公信力"},{"pid":"5e9bbebedd2a30cf4aeddaaa8298ba0854717552","tid":1748663,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:43:18.000Z","msg":"今次係咪冇安排記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6406b0299e33ead09eb416950c1b905a1db5b1","tid":1748663,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T20:44:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"389c02043959a399eb3dd9aabe8aa86b01a0233b","tid":1748663,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T20:48:02.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"1065672aec8168fc0c2d124c1647bc08b2a5587e","tid":1748663,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T20:49:52.000Z","msg":"食早餐好去投啦"}]}